data.description: 20 ac. less than 10 min. from Fbg that offers a freshly remodeled 3bdrm/3 bath main house. Open concept dining & livingroom w/ vaulted ceiling. The kitchen boasts dbl. oven, gas island stovetop, & freshly painted cabinets. Oversized Master bedroom suite w/ walk in closet & fireplace. Freshly painted interior. A large back porch to entertain. A detached 2 car garage with attached 1/1 guesthouse. It is perimeter & crossed fenced. It includes a 30x40 RV barn w/ full hookups, 4 stall barn, pole barn, goat barn, chicken coop, storage buildings and a Dog wash! Perfect horse property or 4h projects.
